## User Story 2.2: Chore Management

**As a** parent  
**I want to** create and manage chores  
**So that** I can assign appropriate tasks to my children

Tasks:

1. Create chore creation interface
2. Implement chore editing functionality
3. Add frequency setting (daily/weekly)
4. Create dollar amount assignment
5. Implement chore assignment to children
6. Add completion criteria setting
